-- Virgile Asia Mining Bids For Aurora's Orkney Gold Operation, Times Reports
-- B y   A n t o n y   S g u a z z i n
-- 2010-11-23T04:53:10Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-23/virgile-asia-mining-bids-for-aurora-s-orkney-gold-operation-times-reports.html
Virgile Asia Mining, a venture
between South African and Chinese investors, has made a bid for
Aurora Empowerment Systems Ltd.’s Orkney gold mine in South
Africa, Johannesburg’s Times newspaper said, citing Hettie
Fourie, a company official.  The bid, which is backed by labor unions and the Industrial
Development Corp., is yet to be considered by liquidators, the
newspaper said, citing Fourie. The IDC is the mine’s main
creditor.    Click here for web link  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
